5. Fix manage_gitlab_ci.yml loop issue too

Where you currently have this:

dest: >-
  {{ repo_environment_init_gitlab_ci_tmpdir.path }}/
  {{ '%02d' | format(ansible_loop.index0 + 1) }}-{{ item.item.name }}.yml

and:

loop_control:
  label: "{{ item.item.name }}"
  extended: true

Change it to this:

dest: >-
  {{ repo_environment_init_gitlab_ci_tmpdir.path }}/
  {{ '%02d' | format(repo_environment_init_fragment_index + 1) }}-{{ item.item.name }}.yml

and:

loop_control:
  label: "{{ item.item.name }}"
  index_var: repo_environment_init_fragment_index

That is safer than relying on ansible_loop.index0.

